{Name}{}{none}
{Speech 1}{}{Pre-dialogue settings}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{player hasn't brought a gun to the guard}
{Speech 1 Answer 9}{}{player brought a gun to the guard earlier, now the guard is favorable to him}
{Speech 2}{}{What do you want?}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{Is it just me, or do you have some kind of problem? }
{Speech 2 Answer 4}{}{Is it just me, or do you have some kind of problem? }
{Speech 3}{}{My problems are none of your business. Get out of here..}
{Speech 3 Answer 5}{}{No, really, something's wrong. Spill it, what happened?}
{Speech 4}{}{Don't linger, go about your business.}
{Speech 5}{}{The thieves have gone completely out of control. I dozed off a bit on duty, and they swiped my gun right away. Just don't tell anyone!}
{Speech 5 Answer 6}{}{What a mess! Tough luck, @sex@|buddy|handsome|, real tough luck. So what now?}
{Speech 6}{}{Well, what now... The chief'll chew me out for sure. I'm afraid they might even kick me out. We're strict about order around here...}
{Speech 6 Answer 7}{}{Maybe I can help you with something?}
{Speech 7}{}{[Looks at you hopefully] Listen... You've got a point there. Maybe you could get me a similar gun? A 10mm pistol, I'll pay 400 coins?}
{Speech 7 Answer 8}{}{No problem! Hand over the coins, I've got that gun.}
{Speech 7 Answer Exit}{}{I'll try to find one, I don't have such a pistol right now.}
